00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:15,160
Bawa mereka pergi.

218
00:24:15,160 --> 00:24:17,030
Baik!

219
00:24:29,020 --> 00:24:30,950
Apa kau baik-baik saja?

220
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,330
Yang Mulia,

221
